text: A Tamagaki is a fence surrounding a Japanese Shinto shrine. Tamagaki may also refer to: *Tamagaki Station, a railway station in Suzuka, Mie, Japan *Tamagaki Gakunosuke (1784 – 1824), a Japanese sumo wrestler *Tamagaki Oyakata (born 1964), a Japanese sumo wrestler and coach
title: Tamagaki (disambiguation)
